{"lemma":"لَحْظَةُ","slug":"لَحْظَةُ","root":"ل.ح.ظ","root_slug":"ل-ح-ظ","root_link":"/words/roots/ل-ح-ظ","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n37639","n37643"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%AD%D9%92%D8%B8%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"moment, instant","tags":["countable"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Instance noun from the root ل ح ظ (l ḥ ẓ)."},"ipa":["/laħ.ðˤa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n37639","headword_ar":"لَحَظَهُ","root":"lHZ","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laHaZahu biAlEayoni","text_ar":"لَحَظَهُ بِالعَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laHaZa A_ilayohi","text_ar":"لَحَظَ اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laHoZN","text_ar":"لَحْظٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laHaZaAnN","text_ar":"لَحَظَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He looked at him from the outer angle of the eye,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the right"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"left,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with more turning of the face than is denoted by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$azorN","text_ar":"شَزْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb, K;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without turning the face:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he watched him with the eye:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) and hence ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mulaAHaZapN","text_ar":"مُلَاحَظَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mufaAEalapN","text_ar":"مُفَاعَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) explained by Az as signifying a man's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"looking from the outer angle of either eye."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","Msb","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n37643","headword_ar":"لَحْظَةٌ","root":"lHZ","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A look from the outer angle of the eye; a sidelong glance; an ogle; a look from the side next the ear:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laHaZaAtN","text_ar":"لَحَظَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": the dim. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luHayoZapN","text_ar":"لُحَيْظَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) Hence the saying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jalasotu Einodahu laHoZapF","text_ar":"جَلَسْتُ عِنْدَهُ لَحْظَةً"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I sat with him the like of"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the time occupied by"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a look from the outer angle of the eye."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY laHoZapK","text_ar":"فِى لَحْظَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In the twinkling of an eye"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"srE","text_ar":"سرع"},{"kind":"text","text":"; &c.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}